casebody.data:
No. 10-7320. Christopher Ysais, Petitioner v. Consuelo Angela Ysais. 562 U.S. 1130, 131 S. Ct. 935,

178 L. Ed. 2d 741,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 503. January 10, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of New Mexico dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
